snippet.title: Bruises by Lewis Capaldi (Cover by Amber Heard)
snippet.description:
Here's my cover of "Bruises" by Lewis Capaldi, hope you enjoy! Its been a while since I last posted a cover but quaratine has given me lots of time to do what I love the most and I hope you’re able to do the same :). 

Instrumental - https://youtu.be/oNeKE9t_1hQ

Please consider donating to these organizations if you're able 
https://www.foodbankscanada.ca/COVID-19.aspx

https://www.canadahelps.org/en/donate-to-coronavirus-outbreak-response/

LINKS
Insta - amberhearrd
Spotify - ambxrheard
Tik tok - amberhearrd 

FAQ's
how old are you? 19
what camera do you use? iphone 8 plus, canon G7x marx 2 or canon powershot ELPH 350 HS
what editing software do you use? imovie and garageband
